[
    {
        "Key": 11.0,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米娅温情提示：",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12.0,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了获得更好的体验，游玩该个人故事前，推荐分析员优先观看《星耀天扉》剧情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "清晨。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "夏日的阳光透过窗帘，褪去了刺眼的光芒，只留下一阵让人舒适的暖意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "感觉到脸上传来的温度，仍在睡梦中的少女下意识抬起了手，想要挡在自己眼前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "片刻后，她却忽然睁大了眼睛，继而猛地直起了身子，从柔软的床上坐了起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呜哇！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "伴随着惊呼声，少女胡乱地在自己的脸上拍了拍，又用力揉了揉双眼，好让自己快速清醒过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么又睡过头了，得赶紧去找分析员才行……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她一边这样说着，一边扭过头想要寻找昨晚脱下的鞋袜。紧接着，她便看到了已经站在床边许久，默默注视着一切发生的我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "早上好，米娅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "眼见我那抑制不住地上扬的嘴角，两抹绯红顿时攀上了米娅的脸颊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还没等我伸手去捏那过于可爱的脸蛋，她已经先一步低下头，将脸深深埋进了枕头里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好丢人————！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "枕头中发出了一阵呜呜声，我则笑着地走到床边坐下，摩挲起她散落在枕头周围的粉色头发。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这有什么丢人的？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "更何况，也不是第一次了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就是因为这样才丢人嘛……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "枕头继续发出了可怜巴巴的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "明明都已经找到分析员了，却还是一直梦到一个人的时候……简直就像长不大的小孩子一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你可一点也不小啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘿嘿，在那方面我还是有自信的——不过我现在说的是年龄哦！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想什么呢，我说的也是年龄。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我抬起手，在她的后脑勺上轻轻敲了两下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "进入歧路宇宙之后，你一个人在这里度过了五年的时间，已经算得上是大人了吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "五年……对哦，已经过去五年了啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "岔开的话题或多或少消解了米娅的羞怯，她总算放过了已经被捏得皱巴巴的枕头，转而抬起那双漂亮的眼睛看向我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也许是因为一直想着分析员的缘故，过去的五年时间，总感觉一转眼就过去了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不用她说我也能猜到，以米娅的性格，自从我们五年前分开的那一刻开始，她一定就将全部的精力放在了找寻我这件事上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这期间所遇到的困难，也绝不是“一转眼”能概括过去的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辛苦你了，米娅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没什么辛苦的啦，分析员为了找到我也做了很多努力吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "硬要说的话，可能有一点遗憾吧，就是那些在路上看到的风景都没来得及记录下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个的话，我倒是有办法解决。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯嗯？真的吗？什么办法？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "先去吃早饭吧，吃完告诉你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员真是的，在这种时候吊我胃口……对了对了！今天的早安吻呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她期待地眨了眨眼睛，我则轻车熟路地低下了头，在她的嘴唇上吻了一下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与米娅重逢后的这一周以来，这成为了我们之间的习惯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在我这样思索着的同时，她忽然伸出双臂，环住了我的脖颈。那双修长的双腿也同时发力，紧紧扣在了我的腰间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "向下看去，米娅整个人都像八爪鱼一样，挂在了我的身上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在，我们去吃早饭吧~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好香好香！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "刚抱着米娅走到餐厅门口，她便已经深深嗅了几下传出的香气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果不是贪恋我怀中的温暖，她恐怕已经扑过去大快朵颐了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我就这样抱着她走到了座椅前，将她轻轻放下，又坐到了她对面的位子上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我拿过餐具的空当，米娅已经将桌上几乎全部的菜肴都品尝了一遍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好吃！！！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "见她露出幸福的笑容，我也忍不住笑了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哎呀分析员你别笑话我嘛，你做的饭菜真的很好吃！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我本来以为，像分析员这样的大忙人，应该没空去磨练厨艺的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你说对了，在此之前我确实不太懂怎么做菜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我一边说着，一边将一块肉放入米娅的碗中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯？分析员的意思是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "和你想的一样，这是我在过去的五年间掌握的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "准确来说，应该也不算是我掌握，归根结底是泰坦物质的功劳。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "泰坦物质……？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米娅正在咀嚼的动作突然停了下来，她面色古怪地低头看向自己的碗中，又眼巴巴地看向至今没有动过筷子的我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员……这些菜，该不会是泰坦物质做成的吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我认真打量了一下她的表情，确定她不是在开玩笑后，才哭笑不得地摇了摇头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然不是了。我的意思是，我利用泰坦物质做了点小设计。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哇呼？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "米娅歪过头，显然没理解我的意思。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你应该知道，在歧路宇宙这样的意识空间中，人的意志可以做到很多现实中做不到的事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我对类似的事情已经很熟悉了，所以在寻找你的途中，也刻意训练了一下自己在这个世界中控制泰坦物质的能力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "结果也很令我满意。有了泰坦物质的辅助，不仅寻找你的效率大大提升了，也获得了一些意外惊喜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我打了个响指，米娅面前的一个空盘便悠悠地漂浮起来，上升到了与米娅视线齐平的高度。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再一挥手，那空盘随即朝着厨房里飞去，自行落在了水槽中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当啷一声，注视着一切发生的米娅在不知不觉间松开了手中的筷子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "米娅星彩",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
